request.description:
Get vaccination plan GROUPED BY AGE.

Response:
{
  "schedulesByAgeGroup": [
    {
      "ageGroupLabel": "Birth",
      "vaccines": [{...}]
    },
    {
      "ageGroupLabel": "6 Weeks",
      "vaccines": [{...}]
    }
  ]
}

Use for: Vaccination Plan Details page with expand/collapse age groups.

Get dashboard data for medical staff home screen.

Returns:
- staff: { id, fullName, firstName, profilePhoto, role, specialization }
- vaccinationCenter: { id, name }
- todayOverview: { totalAppointments, vaccinesGiven, remaining }
- upcomingAppointments: Array (max 5) with:
  - child: { id, name, ageLabel, profilePhoto }
  - ageScheduleLabel (e.g., 'At 6 weeks')
  - dateTimeFormatted (e.g., 'July 15, 2025, 11:29 AM')
  - location, locationType
  - vaccine: { id, name, doseLabel }
  - status
- quickActions: Array of quick action items

Used by: Medical Staff App - Home/Dashboard screen

Get complete appointment details for the Appointment Details screen.

Returns:
- child: { name, dateOfBirth, age, ageLabel, gender, profilePhoto, bloodGroup, allergies, medicalConditions, etc. }
- vaccine: { name, manufacturer, description, dosage, ageGroupLabel, dosageCount, sideEffects }
- doctor: { name, role, specialization }
- date: Formatted date (e.g., 'July 15, 2025')
- time: Time slot (e.g., '09:00 - 10:00 AM')
- vaccinationCenter: { id, name, address, city, phone }
- parent: { fullName, phone, email, relationWithChild, profilePhoto }
- status: Current appointment status
- verificationCode: 4-digit code for check-out validation
- medicalStaff: Assigned staff info

Used by: Medical Staff App - Appointment Details screen

