request.description:
Get available time slots for 30 days from current date. Returns slots from 9 AM to 6 PM (30-min intervals) with availability status for each day.

Returns:
- dateRange: { from, to, totalDays }
- slotInfo: { startTime, endTime, slotDuration, slotsPerDay }
- dates: Array of { date, dayName, slots, availableCount, totalCount }

